Bring your own log analytics (BYOLA) Problem Statement


Customers struggle to diagnose and resolve performance issues​

Customers want absolute usage metrics, at report page level​

​

Limited logs/metrics available in the service (varies by area)​

No long-term storage of performance/health/usage metrics​

Difficult for workspace admins to access relevant data​

Many information sources and tools to get a full picture (inc. 3rd party)​

Correlation is difficult/impossible​

Performance tuning is difficult and time-consuming
